INSTALLATION
============

If you have root on a Unix system it is enough to run this command:

    % cpan Acme::Pythonic

To install this module from the tarball type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install (normally requires root)


DEPENDENCIES
============

This module requires Filter::Simple and Test::More, which are already
included in recent perls.


DOCUMENTATION
=============

Documentation is available the standard way:

    perldoc Acme::Pythonic


